{"tid":53850,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉欣滯留北海道  港人搶毛氈如蝗蟲","createTime":"2016-12-25T04:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T12:38:00.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d21e7cea5c81dfe771fb2e0321691bf6b8244c","tid":53850,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"「食物及毛氈嚴重不足，啲人見到派毛氈，好似蝗蟲搶嘢咁搶」北海道大雪，導致大批旅客滯留新千歲國際機場，數百名香港旅客更要在機場苦等機位。港人Pauline一家三口，原定上周四札幌返港，未料滯留機場，留宿三日，苦不堪言，她不滿地勤派發的食物及毛氈嚴重不足，每次派物資都有人瘋搶，感覺像難民一樣。更令她氣結是航空公司安排失當。<br />\nPauline與丈夫及3歲兒子，於本月17日乘坐國泰CX583往札幌，原定22日返港，但因風雪關係航班取消，他們滯留新千歲國際機場已3日，幾經辛苦爭取，才獲安排今天下午5時返港。她表示，滯留機場期間，地勤分派食物及毛氈又不足，旅客飢寒交迫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Ap5Xqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Ap5Xqk.jpg&h=239e732f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/25/125413_700b4bf9cc5960c0a1c385ce695a170d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F25%2F125413_700b4bf9cc5960c0a1c385ce695a170d.jpg&h=79b859de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bbc7e52d0a93cc1f46c439f6e21ac9f5e3a3dbe","tid":53850,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bc1ec6f904017254391415795663620335a418","tid":53850,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"睇錯港人毛毛蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}